                    "node": {
                        "created_at": "1767920050",
                        "id": "18318049006221361",
                        "text": "I had some of the best bites of pasta in my entire life! Eating at fileja was both a delicious and riveting experience. I enjoyed watching the chef meticulously craft each piece of pasta while also making sure that they were cooked perfectly al dente. It\u2019s been a few months since my visit, but I still think about the pasta here.\u2063\n\u2063\nThe courses in their pasta omakase do change based on the season. I hope to come back again in the future to try even more pasta. Thank you to @roaming.eater for the amazing recommendation!\u2063\n\u2063\n\ud83d\udccd fileja (@fileja2021)\u2063\nJapan, \u3012101-0041 Tokyo, Chiyoda City, Kanda Sudacho, 2 Chome\u221213\u22121 \u30ce\u30eb\u30f3\u79cb\u8449\u539f\u30d3\u30eb 1\u968e\u968e\u2063\n\u2063\n\u2063\n\u2063\n#pasta #italianfood #tokyofood #tokyotrip #omakase"
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
